{"tid":1641275,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"指學生為暴徒 理大香港專上學院講師陳偉強被暫時停止職務","createTime":"2019-10-09T09:43:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T09:55:56.000Z","uid":212626,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2e26797a79b83609869242981f07552298c03d7c","tid":1641275,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:43:36.000Z","msg":"香港理工大學香港專上學院在西九龍校園舉行師生對話會，約600人出席，學生就講師陳偉強指責學生是暴徒的言論提出關注。<br />\n<br />\n交流大會結束後，香港專上學院學生會內務副會長謝子樂說，<span style=\"color: red;\">校方暫時停止講師陳偉強本學期的職務</span>，亦表示會尊重講師的言論自由，不會強迫他道歉。校方希望學生及老師可以包容不同政見，亦需要數星期以調查陳偉強的有關言論。<br />\n<br />\n謝子樂稱，不滿意校方的安排，學生要求與陳偉強直接對話，但他昨日多次拒絕回應學生的提問，今日亦缺席交流會，期望校方為雙方建構對話平台，下星期紅磡灣校園亦會有類似的交流大會。<br />\n<br />\n香港理工大學校董會成員李傲然說，警方進入校園必須跟校方聯絡及得到批准，但若警方強行進入並進行拘捕，校方表示會根據事件的嚴重程度作決定。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485181-20191009.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485181-20191009.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNu6xA88r%2B4g6PmjrNIuMcHw%3D&h=236c7b0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485181-20191009.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a00be05b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485181-20191009.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"a201bae28c144dc19d2f50453b9a226c85d02e21","tid":1641275,"uid":80200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:43:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"797b4b73b336636f3daeeaa85ba270d20eb9eeb9","tid":1641275,"uid":134774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:44:19.000Z","msg":"一大"},{"pid":"d8fff17606407d3a7c32b9565a84fd6456a2aa1d","tid":1641275,